data.description:
Waterfront access to Trailwood Lake inlet.  This 4 bedroom 3.5 bath home was completely updated in 2017.

*Master Bedroom has two walk in closets, whirlpool tub, separate shower
*Bedroom #2 - has own bath with walk in closet
*Bedroom #3- has own bath/shower with walk in closet
*Formal Dining room
*Large Kitchen with stainless steel appliances, 2 ovens and walk in pantry 
*Butler’s pantry
*Large laundry room with sink and island
*Home Office
*Upstairs Playroom/Bedroom 
*Upstairs storage room
*Enclosed two car garage (with storage room)
*Large Covered back patio or entertaining 

Call today for your private showing!
data.whatILove: Award winning Petal School District, close to shopping.  Sits nestled on 1.10 mol wooded acres in sought after  Trailwood Subdiviom.  Lots of room for a large family or for a family to grow.
